### 2. List All Packages (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/packages
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get Specific Package Details (Copy an ID from the list above)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/packages/your-id-here
Content-Type: application/json

